**Example 1: GetConsortiumList**

获取联盟列表

Input: 

```
tccli tdid GetConsortiumList --cli-unfold-argument ```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "ConsortiumList": [
            {
                "Id": 661,
                "Name": "TDID测试"
            }
        ],
        "RequestId": "41a9acae-cef4-4949-b144-48c65ad5e425"
    }
}
```
